text: Veins of the World () is a 2020 Mongolian German drama movie directed by Byambasuren Davaa and starring Bat-Ireedui Batmunkh, Enerel Tumen, Yalalt Namsrai, Algirchamin Baatarsuren, Ariunbyamba Sukhee. == Other websites == * Category:2020 drama movies Category:Mongolian movies Category:German drama movies Category:Movies directed by Byambasuren Davaa
title: Veins of the World
